Get all Census tracts within a given ZIP code

get_tracts.Rd

Get all Census tracts within a given ZIP code

get_tracts(zip_code)

Arguments

zip_code

A U.S. ZIP code

Value

dataframe of Census tracts and data from Census crosswalk file found for given ZIP code

Examples

get_tracts('08731')
